xorg-legacy-fonts: Xorg Legacy Fonts
xorg-legacy-fonts:
xorg-legacy-fonts: Xorg's ancestor (X11R1, in 1987) at first only provided bitmap 
xorg-legacy-fonts: fonts, with a tool (bdftopcf) to assist in their installation. With 
xorg-legacy-fonts: the introduction of xorg-server-1.19.0 and libXfont2 many people 
xorg-legacy-fonts: will not need them. 
xorg-legacy-fonts:  + font-adobe-100dpi
xorg-legacy-fonts:  + font-adobe-75dpi
xorg-legacy-fonts:  + font-jis-misc
xorg-legacy-fonts:  + font-daewoo-misc
xorg-legacy-fonts:  + font-isas-misc
